OL,3,CNursery worker jailed for more than
OL,4,Cthree years over death of toddler
OL,6,FA nursery worker has been jailed for
OL,7,Fthree years and four months over the
OL,8,Fdeath of a 14-month-old toddler who
OL,9,Fsuffocated while staff tried to make
OL,10,Fhim fall asleep.
OL,12,FNoah Sibanda died after the incident
OL,13,Fat Fairytales Day Nursery in Bourne
OL,14,FStreet in Dudley, having been
OL,15,Fphysically restrained face down on a
OL,16,Fcushion with a blanket over his face
OL,17,Fand a leg placed over him.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776531953
OL,3,CNursery worker jailed for more than
OL,4,Cthree years over death of toddler
OL,6,FNursery practitioner Kimberley
OL,7,FCookson, 23, admitted gross negligence
OL,8,Fmanslaughter in relation to her
OL,9,Factions in trying to make the toddler
OL,10,Fsleep on December 9th, 2022.
OL,12,FThe nursery's owner, Deborah Latewood,
OL,13,F55, has been sentenced to six months
OL,14,Fin prison, suspended for two years.
OL,16,FShe had admitted a Health and Safety
OL,17,Fat Work Act offence on the basis that
OL,18,Fshe did not know ` but should have
OL,19,Fknown ` children were being put down
OL,20,Fto sleep in a dangerous way.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776531953
OL,3,CNursery worker jailed for more than
OL,4,Cthree years over death of toddler
OL,6,FThe company that ran the nursery,
OL,7,FFairytales Day Nursery Limited, has
OL,8,Fbeen fined #240,000, with the judge
OL,9,Fnoting that the risk of death had been
OL,10,F"highly foreseeable."
OL,12,FLast month, it admitted one count of
OL,13,Fcorporate manslaughter and a Health
OL,14,Fand Safety at Work Act offence at
OL,15,FWolverhampton Crown Court.
OL,17,FThe CPS said the incident, which was
OL,18,Fcaptured on CCTV at the nursery, saw
OL,19,FNoah tightly wrapped in a sleeping bag
OL,20,Fwith a blanket over his head and laid
OL,21,Fface down to sleep by Cookson.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@UO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776531953
OL,3,CNursery worker jailed for more than
OL,4,Cthree years over death of toddler
OL,6,FShe is said to have held the toddler
OL,7,Fface down on a cushion and restrained
OL,8,Fhim with her leg for some of that
OL,9,Ftime, in what the CPS said appeared to
OL,10,Fbe an effort to "make him sleep when
OL,11,Fhe did not want to".
OL,13,FNoah was then found not to be
OL,14,Fbreathing and 999 was called, but he
OL,15,Fwas pronounced dead in hospital.
OL,17,FPassing sentence on Friday, High Court
OL,18,FJudge Mr Justice Choudhury said:
OL,19,F"Tragically, the events of that day
OL,20,Fmeant that Mr and Mrs Sibanda would
OL,21,Fnever see Noah alive again.
OL,26,@rD@QOUsD@SO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776531953
OL,3,CNursery worker jailed for more than
OL,4,Cthree years over death of toddler
OL,6,F"The court has been shown CCTV footage
OL,7,Fof the baby room. The images on that
OL,8,Ffootage can only be described as
OL,9,Fshocking.
OL,11,F"There were repeated instances of
OL,12,Frough handling of babies by several of
OL,13,Fthe nursery practitioners, including
OL,14,FMiss Cookson, often in view of a
OL,15,Fmanager."
OL,17,FThe judge said babies had been
OL,18,Frepeatedly tightly swaddled and then
OL,19,Fbeen covered in blankets or cloth in
OL,20,Fwhat was an "established" practice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@IO]|D@MOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776531953
OL,3,CNursery worker jailed for more than
OL,4,Cthree years over death of toddler
OL,6,F"Not once did any practitioner
OL,7,Fchallenge another about this practice.
OL,8,FThese dangerous and unacceptable
OL,9,Fpractices, which went unchecked at his
OL,10,Fnursery, reached their inevitable
OL,11,Fconclusion on the 9th of December
OL,12,F2022."
OL,14,FThe level of disregard for Noah's
OL,15,Fwelfare was distressing to watch, the
OL,16,Fjudge said, with the "horrible truth"
OL,17,Fbeing that Noah was probably
OL,18,Funconscious after he stopped moving at
OL,19,Faround 1:10pm on December 9.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@FO]xD@VOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776531953
OL,3,CNursery worker jailed for more than
OL,4,Cthree years over death of toddler
OL,6,FVictim impact statements were read to
OL,7,Fthe court by junior prosecution
OL,8,Fcounsel Daniel Cordey during a hearing
OL,9,Fon Thursday.
OL,11,FIn the statements, Noah's mother Masi
OL,12,Fdescribed his birth as "a prayer
OL,13,Fanswered" and spoke of how he had
OL,14,Fbrought a calmness to her life.
OL,16,FDescribing how she had left Noah in
OL,17,Fthe care of staff she thought would
OL,18,Flook after him, she said: "I handed
OL,19,FNoah over to the people who killed him.
OL,26,@tD@XOUuD@IO]zD@[OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776531953
OL,3,CNursery worker jailed for more than
OL,4,Cthree years over death of toddler
OL,6,F"Because of this I cannot forgive
OL,7,Fmyself and consequently will never
OL,8,Fforgive the defendants."
OL,10,FShe added of the nursery: "Behind
OL,11,Fclosed doors they were playing Russian
OL,12,Froulette with our children's lives."
OL,14,FIn a separate statement, Noah's father
OL,15,FThulani said: "My son died at just 14-
OL,16,Fmonths-old because of the gross
OL,17,Fnegligence of someone who was trusted
OL,18,Fto care for him.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@XO]rD@[OUtD@dO]wD@OOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776531953
OL,3,CNursery worker jailed for more than
OL,4,Cthree years over death of toddler
OL,6,F"When a child is taken from this world
OL,7,Fthe loss is immeasurable. Noah's
OL,8,Fabsence is felt in every corner of our
OL,9,Flives.
OL,11,F"Noah deserved to live. He deserved to
OL,12,Fbe protected and we deserved to watch
OL,13,Fhim grow up."
OL,15,FFairytales Day Nursery was also
OL,16,Fordered to pay #56,000 in costs by the
OL,17,Fjudge, who told Cookson: "In my
OL,18,Fjudgment Noah's suffering may not have
OL,19,Fbeen obvious to you but it ought to
OL,20,Fhave been.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@MO]yD@ZOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776531953
OL,3,CNursery worker jailed for more than
OL,4,Cthree years over death of toddler
OL,6,F"This is not a case where you
OL,7,Fknowingly set out to suffocate or
OL,8,Fasphyxiate.
OL,10,F"You are clearly remorseful.
OL,12,F"You have attempted to understand that
OL,13,FNoah's parents are the real sufferers
OL,14,Fhere.
OL,16,F"You have not sought to blame others."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
