PN,37711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776531953
OL,3,CNursery worker jailed for more than
OL,4,Cthree years over death of toddler
OL,6,FOfsted, which ordered the nursery to
OL,7,Fclose shortly after the incident, said
OL,8,Fin a statement: "Our thoughts remain
OL,9,Fwith Noah's family and we are deeply
OL,10,Fsorry for their loss.
OL,12,F"No child should ever come to harm in
OL,13,Fa place that is meant to keep them
OL,14,Fsafe.
OL,16,F"The Government has recently announced
OL,17,Fnew funding to allow us to inspect
OL,18,Fnurseries more frequently and we
OL,19,Fcontinually review our work, alongside
OL,20,Four partners, to help make nurseries
OL,21,Fas safe as they can be for children."
OL,26,@pD@QOUtD@AOUxD@AOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
